note bottom
  This diagram represents the logical AI / Graduate Knowledge view.
  The tables are physically stored in the same PostgreSQL database as the Core Application database but are documented separately for readability.
  Current SQL retrieval reads the V24 canonical model: university, faculty, department, degree_type, language, source, graduate_program, aliases, tracks, program sources, tuition, admissions, documents, and their related knowledge tables.
  Campus/location is represented by university.campus_name, university.campus_type, city, latitude, and longitude; no separate campus or location table exists.
end note
